column5: Morning folks...  Can anyone give me a hand and guide me through the steps of how to load the Ibycus maps to my Garmin 76CX??......I saved the Ibycus winzip file to my PC...not sure where to go from here     ...any help would be appreciated!!  Steve

Extract the zip file and you will end up with file ending in ISO.  The ISO file is a compiled DVD image, Open your DVD burning software and from the menu find the option to burn an image or open image file.  Then burn.  You will end up with a DVD that has many files on it including instruction files.  With Regards,  forrest
